	   <tr><td colspan=2>Both items dropped are No Drop, and count as half of the Fiery Avenger quest.&nbsp;&nbsp;The robe, as Adraii said, is very nice, with the head being...a head.  To get Miragul to spawn, you must give Miragul's Lich a "Phylactery", which you get from the Oracle of Karnon, to get that you must give the Tome of Scale (i think) to the Oracle.  To get the tome, you must kill Nagafen & Vox, to get both halves of the Tome of Scale.  Give these halves, and 1000pp, to the female Tobiath that does a part of the Gleaming Torch quest.  A little confusing, no?  Miragul is as strong as a Dragon, and has a pet to boot.  Reccomended party to take him: Everyone you can get.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
